        "TileImage": "$($repository 6ca02d70-ce2d-467f-a908-f6b93b685f38).Image",
        "Description": "Tamara Vidal, current Argentine political operative and former CIA asset, is threatening to release compromising information on a CIA informant network within the Argentine government and media. 47, you have been contracted to discredit her by the CIA. Eliminate her henchmen and get her alone. Once you&apos;ve rendered her unconscious, install the SIM card provided by our client on her phone. The CIA will take over remotely from that point on. Good luck, 47.",
